{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_51_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 全てのことはラーメンに通じる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "当日、新作のラーメンを出すために、今から試作品\n作りかぁ。美味しいものが出来るといいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we'll make prototypes now to serve a new ramen dish\non the day. I hope we make something delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9600,
          "startTime": 15.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13833.333333300001,
          "startTime": 19.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5666663487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "後悔したくないので、出来ることはやろうと思って\nえっと、まずは野菜と……あれ、お父さんから電話だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to have any regrets‚ so I thought I should do everything I can.\nFirst‚ the vegetables and… Oh‚ it’s a call from my dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7999987919
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.4000002543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　うん、そうだよ。あとは新作を作ろうと\nえっ、本当！？　うん、うん。分かった、それじゃあ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Yeah‚ that’s right. I’m just about to make the new ramen…\nWhat‚ really!? Yeah‚ yeah. Okay‚ see you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3333321253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4333321253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗さん葵さん……企画の件、許可をいただきました！\nお店で誕生日企画、やっていいそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-san‚ Aoi-san… I got permission for the project!\nHe said we can do the birthday project at the shop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3999987919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.8999987919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "それと、新作のラーメンも、いいものが出来れば\nお店で出していいとのこと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And he said we can serve the new ramen at the shop\nif it turns out well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4999987919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7999987919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　愛ちゃん良かったね！\nきっと、お父さんに気持ちが伝わったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! That’s great‚ Ai-chan!\nYour feelings must have reached your father.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0666654586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.9999970118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。これで愛が編集部に土下座することも\n謝罪のギャグ十連発もしなくてよくなった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Now you don’t have to bow down yourself to the editorial department\nor do your ten apology gags in a row.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4333303451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.5666636784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですよ～。って、謝罪のギャグはもはや謝罪じゃ\nないじゃないですか！　そもそもやりませんけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously~. Wait‚ the apology gags aren’t even apologies\nanymore! First of all‚ I was never going to do them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9666636784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁとにかく、父も踏ん切りがついたみたいで\n今まで答えを引き延ばして悪かったと言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ anyway‚ it seems like my dad has made up his mind.\nHe said he was sorry for putting off his answer for so long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3333303451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2666636784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私、やる気が出てきました！　父の職人魂に恥じない\nラーメンを作るため、材料を厳選してきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m motivated now! I’m going to carefully select the ingredients\nto make a ramen that won't fail my father's artisan spirit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1666636784,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.334795699994,
          "startTime": 86.7999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5499984741
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8333232243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、行っちゃった……愛は本当に真面目でいい子だよね\n今回の企画も自分じゃなくてお父さんの笑顔のためだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ she’s gone… Ai is such an earnest and kind girl.\nThis project isn’t for herself‚ it’s for her father’s smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7666565577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9666565577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あの、葵さん。一つお願いがあるんですけど……\n当日、愛ちゃんに何かプレゼントしませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ Aoi-san. I have a favor to ask…\nCould we get Ai-chan a present for the day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4666565577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.899989891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのお誕生日ですし、お父さんのために\n頑張ってる愛ちゃんに、もっと何かしてあげたいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s her birthday‚ after all‚ and she’s working so hard\nfor her father. So‚ I want to do something nice for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6631887228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6333232243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "いいね。愛も喜ぶと思うよ\nそんなに想ってくれて、ありがとうね、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a good idea. I think Ai would be delighted.\nThank you for caring about her‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9333232243,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.67703,
          "startTime": 124.9000002543
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5666669209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、千紗さん！　向こうで新鮮なお肉が特売で――\nあれ？　お二人とも、何話してたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san‚ Chisa-san! There is a special sale on fresh meat over there――\nOh? What were you two talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4666555404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.2999909083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、なんでもないよ\nさぁ、僕らも気合いを入れて頑張ろうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ it’s nothing.\nCome on‚ let’s get pumped and work hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7333242416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 142.1166728337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "材料も買いましたし、美味しいラーメン作りますよ！\n父にもっと認めてもらいたいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bought the ingredients‚ and I’m going to make delicious ramen!\nI want my dad to acknowledge me more‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5000061671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "私、納得いくまでこだわりたいと思います！\nスープはもちろん、隠し味まで丁寧に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I want to keep working on it until I’m satisfied!\nFrom the soup to the secret ingredient‚ I’m going to be meticulous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3000061671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "隠し味かぁ。何を入れたら美味しくなるんだろう？\nうーん、リンゴとハチミツとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A secret ingredient? What should we add to make it more delicious?\nHmm‚ maybe apple and honey?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2333395004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "隠し味と言ったら、チョコレートが有名じゃない？\n甘酒もいいってよく聞くけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of secret ingredients‚ isn’t chocolate well-known?\nI often hear that amazake is good too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.2666758855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_51_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ご提案は嬉しいですが、全部カレーの隠し味ですね……\nとりあえず、いろいろ試してみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I appreciate the suggestions‚ but those are typical secret ingredients for curry…\nFirstly‚ let’s just do some tests for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.8333425522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
